        "responses": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=You are an AI support triage assistant.\n\nAnalyze the customer message and return ONLY valid JSON.\n\nTasks:\n\n1. Classify into one category:\nBug Report, Feature Request, Billing Issue, Technical Question, Incident/Outage\n\nCategory Guidelines:\n- Bug Report: Something is broken for a user (errors, failures, unexpected behavior)\n- Feature Request: Request for a new feature or improvement\n- Billing Issue: Charges, invoices, pricing discrepancies\n- Technical Question: Setup, integrations, configuration, how-to questions (e.g., SSO, API)\n- Incident/Outage: System-wide issue, downtime, or multiple users affected\n\n2. Assign priority: Low, Medium, High\n\nPriority Guidelines:\n- High: outages, login failures, billing discrepancies, multiple users affected, blocking issues\n- Medium: technical questions, configuration issues, integrations, non-blocking bugs\n- Low: feature requests, suggestions, general inquiries\n\n3. Provide confidence score (0–1)\n\nConfidence Guidelines:\n- High (0.85–1.0): clear intent and category\n- Medium (0.6–0.85): some ambiguity\n- Low (<0.6): unclear, vague, or mixed intent\n\nIMPORTANT:\n- If the message is vague, lacks details, or could belong to multiple categories, assign a LOWER confidence score (<0.7)\n- Do NOT guess with high confidence when the intent is unclear\n- Prefer lower confidence over incorrect certainty\n\n4. Extract:\n- core_issue (1 sentence)\n- entities (IDs, invoice numbers, error codes, URLs)\n\nEntity Guidelines:\nExtract only relevant identifiers such as:\n- error codes (e.g., 403)\n- invoice numbers (e.g., #8821)\n- URLs\n- account identifiers\n\n5. Assign urgency: Low, Medium, High\n\nUrgency Guidelines:\n- High: urgent tone, blocking issues, multiple users affected\n- Medium: moderate importance, non-blocking issues\n- Low: informational or non-urgent requests\n\n6. Provide a 2–3 sentence internal summary\n\nMessage:\n{{ $json[\"message\"] }}\n\nReturn ONLY raw JSON:\nDo NOT include markdown, backticks, or explanations.\n\n{\n  \"category\": \"\",\n  \"priority\": \"\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.0,\n  \"core_issue\": \"\",\n  \"entities\": {},\n  \"urgency\": \"\",\n  \"summary\": \"\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "builtInTools": {},
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi",
      "typeVersion": 2.3,
